{"tid":62269,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"(新手) PHP + MySQL 問題","createTime":"2016-12-31T18:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T22:12:36.000Z","uid":19903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b877e413fd866c3cbc0ce2173486da00d9cf277","tid":62269,"uid":19903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:22:51.000Z","msg":"各位新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的 小弟新手上路用 HTML 整左個 form <br />\n可以填完 form 就寫啲 data 入 MySQL <br />\n奈何我 update 完之後依家唔 work<br />\n同時又發現到有些少安全性問題<br />\n所以打算斬掉重練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇咩其他方法可以做到以上效果<br />\n而又唔多唔少比較安全少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：超外行 有錯勿屌 求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c7a64821a0464b653a82f8cae0ead9d3ce6478","tid":62269,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:10:25.000Z","msg":"&quot;填完 form 就寫啲 data 入 MySQL&quot;<br />\n要搵死因嘅話<br />\n1. 叫 PHP 行完句SQL statement, output mysql error, 睇下咩事<br />\n2. echo句SQL statement出嚟睇下有冇錯, 自己貼落phpMyAdmin試行, 睇下咩事<br />\nOtherwise一係PHP根本冇行到去1., 或你句SQL logic有問題"},{"pid":"31e18bd1d79b0a6050c496f2ca4ad795f727907f","tid":62269,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:18:51.000Z","msg":"要安全<br />\n用prepared statement防SQL injection<br />\nPDO有呢樣嘢<br />\n或者用Framework, 如CodeIgniter, 其實重方便, 但新手適應有啲難度"},{"pid":"5ad8de7e175fae43ed3ad8b2595d162aa69ffafa","tid":62269,"uid":19903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T20:00:03.000Z","msg":"感謝兩位巴打既回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為之前個 setting 係 run 完個 php file 即刻 header 去某個預定既 HTML page <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以無視左 個 error message <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩睇返發現係我加左 auto increment 但冇係 insert 個 values 寫返 null <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該曬兩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c4d26d09f3e076b2d83254bd095072d8459972","tid":62269,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T21:17:55.000Z","msg":"樓主有陰陽眼?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92040cae1c79c068594d61c7d9c73d81a87515ae","tid":62269,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T21:20:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感謝兩位巴打既回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為之前個 setting 係 run 完個 php file 即刻 header 去某個預定既 HTML page <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以無視左 個 error message <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩睇返發現係我加左 auto increment 但冇係 insert 個 values 寫返 null <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該曬兩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你行一次你句SQL睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c9d9344f1747e807965074c4c51ced783110c1","tid":62269,"uid":19903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T22:03:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>感謝兩位巴打既回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br /